                        "description": "Returns an array of all planes currently in the system.\n\n**Route:** `GET /api/planes` → `PlaneController@index`\n\nNo parameters, no request body required.\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Response 200 OK\nReturns a `status` field and a `data` array of all plane objects.\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": [\n    { \"id\": 1, \"model\": \"Boeing 747\", \"airline\": \"Ukraine International\" },\n    { \"id\": 2, \"model\": \"Airbus A320\", \"airline\": \"Wizz Air\" },\n    { \"id\": 3, \"model\": \"Antonov 225\", \"airline\": \"Antonov Dream Airlines\" },\n    { \"id\": 4, \"model\": \"Antonov 124\", \"airline\": \"Antonov Dream Airlines\" }\n  ]\n}\n```"
                    },
