                        "description": "Returns a single plane record by its integer ID.\n\n**Route:** `GET /api/planes/{id}` → `PlaneController@show`\n\n---\n\n### 📥 Path Parameter\n| Name | Type | Required | Description |\n|------|------|----------|-------------|\n| id | integer | ✅ yes | Unique plane ID |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Response 200 OK\nReturns the plane object directly (no wrapper).\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"model\": \"Boeing 747\",\n  \"airline\": \"Ukraine International\"\n}\n```\n\n### ❌ Response 404 Not Found\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": \"Resource not found\",\n  \"message\": \"Plane with ID 99 does not exist\"\n}\n```"
